      "body": "html5:stream 使用 jsonp 报`ReferenceError: Can't find variable: global`  \r\ndemo: http://dotwe.org/vue/74dfe8a47895e4581963a9b6b2e0a46e\r\n\r\nweek版本:\r\n```\r\n   v1.0.1-beta.5\r\n - weex-builder : v0.1.16\r\n```\r\n\r\n看了 #1175 #1055 没有找到解决办法\r\n\r\n临时解决方法：修改了`node_modules/weex-vue-render`\r\n```\r\nfunction _jsonp (config, callback, progressCallback) {\r\n  var cbName = 'jsonp_' + (++jsonpCnt);\r\n  var url;\r\n\r\n  if (!config.url) {\r\n    console.error('[h5-render] config.url should be set in _jsonp for \\'fetch\\' API.');\r\n  }\r\n // 临时解决\r\n  var global = _global;\r\n\r\n  global[cbName] = (function (cb) {\r\n     ...\r\n  })(cbName);\r\n```\r\n"
